<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 27 at 3:03PM EST  by NWS Detroit</headline>
<description>...PATCHY DENSE FOG THIS AFTERNOON...
Areas of fog will persist across the region leading into the rush
hour commute. Fog may become dense in some locations, leading to
visibilities of one half mile or less. Drivers should be prepared
for rapidly fluctuating visibilities and the possibility of
variable roadway conditions. Slow down and allow plenty of
distance between you and the vehicle in front of you.</description>
